    "description": "Grow your career with V-Mart Retail! We are hiring a Department Manager for our Faridabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout V-Mart Retail:\nV-Mart Retail is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with V-Mart Retail!",
